# 🎓 College Project Access Portal - Backend

This is the backend for a College Project Portal developed using *Node.js, **Express.js, and **MongoDB Atlas*.  
It allows students to:
- View project details
- Verify their identity using student ID cards via OCR
- Securely access project data based on college affiliation

---

## 🔧 Technologies Used

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB Atlas
- Mongoose
- Tesseract.js (OCR)
- Multer (file uploads)
- dotenv

---

## 📦 API Endpoints

### 📁 Project APIs
- GET /api/projects – Get all project details

### 📄 Student Verification (OCR)
- POST /api/verify/verify-id  
  Upload a student ID card and get the college name using OCR.

